------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  L38 DCONV       Dry adiabatic adjustment?                 y/n
  L39 MCONV       Moist convection scheme?                  y/n

Separator lines (explicitly read & discarded):
  L40 (skip) blank
  L41 (skip) blank

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
