------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  L42 FLUXSWITCH  Turbulent surface fluxes on/off           y/n
  L43 BETA        Fraction of surface covered by water      0–1
  L44 DEPTH       Mixed-layer depth                          m
  L45 VS0         Surface wind speed                         m s^-1
                 - For HW (c): this is the knob to vary wind speed

Separator lines (explicitly read & discarded):
