  L47 (skip) blank

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Imposed large-scale vertical motion profile (omega) (lines 48–55)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  L48 WCUBE       Use cubic profile of omega?               y/n
  L49 WMAX        Extreme value of omega                    hPa hour^-1
                 (negative = upward motion)
  L50 PERIOD      Period of omega variation                 days
  L51 PWZERO      Pressure where omega = 0 (top)            hPa
  L52 PWBOTTOM    Pressure where omega = 0 (bottom)         hPa
  L53 PWMAX       Pressure where omega reaches extreme      hPa

Separator lines (explicitly read & discarded):
  L54 (skip) blank
  L55 (skip) blank

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Weak Temperature Gradient (WTG) mode (lines 56–59)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  L56 WTG         Apply WTG approximation?                  y/n
  L57 PFIX        Pressure above which sounding fixed       hPa

  L58 blank (not read)
  L59 blank (not read)

